INSTALL

Enable Extension

Add the following code into the default notification template you use.

{def $last_version=fetch( bccontentdiffnotifications, last_archived_version, hash( id, $object.contentobject_id ) )}
{def $diff=fetch( bccontentdiffnotifications, diff_versions, hash( object, $nd, lastversion, $last_version ) )}
{$diff}


Add the above template code into the template, design/standard/templates/notification/handler/ezsubtree/view/plain.tpl


Clear Cache
